1. *Spasi* ga od te propasti! (Save him from this ruin!)
2. Ona će učiniti sve da *spase* njegov život. (She will do everything to save his life.)
3. Moramo brzo da *spasimo* tu situaciju. (We have to quickly save this situation.)
4. *Spašavao* je sve što je mogao. (He was saving everything he could.)
5. Ljudi su se trudili da *spase* životinje. (People were trying to save the animals.)